        "The world will know the only name",
        "In which the Saints can trust."
      ]
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "lines": [
        "When he comes down from heav\u2019n to earth",
        "With all his holy band,",
        "Before creation\u2019s second birth,",
        "We hope with him to stand."
      ]
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "lines": [
